			<description source="Sridevi Padmanabhan," lang="en" script="latn">An image with the title "Friends" in a sample calender poster of the Empire Calender Manufacturing Co., Calcutta depicting two women sitting on a couch and chatting while drinking tea. The side table holds a white ceramic tea set with containers for tea, milk and sugar. Both of them hold steaming cups of tea in tea cups with saucers in their hands. In the background, the lower part of an image with a European-style landscape can be seen on the wall.</description>
